missionSettings.description: A campaign of island hopping, in which BDF and PALA fight for control of the Ignus Archipelago.Your mission is to take and hold the Feldspar International Airport and surrounding smaller airstrips, and to sufficiently degrade the enemy's ability to launch further attacks.

Data.StringValue: PALA forces have been removed from the mainland and BDF holds the surrounding airstrips. BDF Is Victorious.
BDF forces have been removed from the mainland and PALA holds the surrounding airstrips. PALA Is Victorious.
